room_title: Escape room "Fried Chicken" by 21 Keys Escape Rooms in Colorado Springs
room_address: 3362 Templeton Gap Rd, Colorado Springs, CO 80907
room_description:
As a member of Interpol's elite artifact recovery unit, you've just received critical information regarding your next mission. Critical? Hardly. You've heard this same story time and again. Find artifact. Return to owner. Blah, blah, blah. Just another day.
Then you read the fine print: a Colorado Springs artist-gone-bad, a missing rubber chicken, and a mysterious ode to some kind of toaster pastry. What? That can't be right. Probably ought to go check it out.
